				                <div><p>I just figured this out. I was having the same problem as others&nbsp;setting up email on&nbsp;my Galaxy S4. Here's how to&nbsp;fix the problem.</p>
<p>1. Look at the IMAP server field where your email address will be&nbsp;generated&nbsp;as imap.email address.com.</p>
