<p>3. Do the same for the outgoing email field of SMPT (when you get to it).&nbsp;</p>
<p>4. If needed,&nbsp;look in cPanel to see what&nbsp;ports to use. Mine&nbsp;for IMAP (incoming mail) is 143 and SMPT&nbsp;(outgoing mail)&nbsp;is 25 (you may need to manually change this).</p>
<p>5.&nbsp;Make sure as stated&nbsp;in the above directions&nbsp;to use&nbsp;your full email address&nbsp;in the email address field as well as the Username field.</p>
