2. CHANGE the word imap to the word mail. <br />
3. Do the same for the outgoing email field of SMPT (when you get to it). <br />
4. If needed, look in cPanel to see what ports to use. Mine for IMAP (incoming mail) is 143 and SMPT (outgoing mail) is 25 (you may need to manually change this).<br />
5. Make sure as stated in the above directions to use your full email address in the email address field as well as the Username field.<br />
