<li>Since I have seen clients drop/change settings, double check your <a href="http://www.inmotionhosting.com/support/edu/everything-email/introduction-email/how-to-find-email-settings">email settings</a> for any issues, or mispellings.</li><br />
<li>Check with your host to ensure they did not modify your account. For example they may moved you to a new server, or changed your email password if it appears to be compromised, or spamming.</li><br />
